The 24th annual South African Music Awards are just around the corner. As we get closer and closer to the big day, the organisers of SAMAs are revealing their top five category nominations.  The nominees for the Best Male of the Year and Best Female of the Year award have now been announced. In the running for the Best Male gong are: AfrotractionEmteeNduduzo MakhathiniPrince KaybeeTresor. The Best Female category is made up of: BusiswaLady ZamarShekhinahSimphiwe DanaSiphokazi. The SAMA award ceremony takes place in Sun City, North West on June 2 2018.  